name: 迪伦乔治亚兹
name_full: 迪伦乔治亚兹 Dylan Georgiades
introduction: Dylan Jett Georgiades was born on September 19th 2002 in Melbourne, Australia. From the time he could talk he has displayed obvious talents in acting, comedy, singing and dancing. Dylan has had appearances in Australian television shows including 'Rove Live' and 'Talking About Your Generation', as well as several TV commercials and voice overs. Dylan is a talented pianist and vocalist, and performed with the Varety Youth Performance Group. He lives in Melbourne with his mother Debbi (a Wedding Singer), father Petros (Audio Engineer & Composer) and his older brother Jesse. The Water Diviner is Dylan's first major movie role.
